About

Est. 2026 in Lowville, NY.

Marziale Technologies conducts research and solves a wide set of technological problems for the purpose of advancing civilization in New York's North Country. It is led by Dr. Joseph Marziale, former GA-3 at Los Alamos National Laboratory.

Clients include Pixamation, Flack Broadcasting, Shue Brothers, The Raven's Quill, New York Pizzeria, and Red Barn Meats.
